    public class EnumParser<T extends Enum<T>>
extends FileBasedDictionaryParser<T>
    Generic parser for enumerations making use of our vocabulary util to lookup an enum value from a string. Also adds stronger normalization removing any non-ASCII-alphanumeric characters. It is still ok to use hyphens or underscores in the enumeration values.
